rtion\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3464}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She needed to merge both halves, find peace and speed simultaneously.\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both halves\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0089\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0089how?\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0089\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Gameswere only 11 months away.\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Gameswere\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu reached peak joy in Tokyo, at those Olympics, where she sprinted across the widest, grandest stage of her career.\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9697248958409214, \"rank\": 0.031220297966924618, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"peak joy\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"those Olympics\", \"from\": 3645, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"the widest, grandest stage\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Aug. 3, 2021, she became the first American woman to win 800-meter gold at the Games in more than half a century.\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3767, \"end\": 3781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.181772238