ngram\": \"a steak knife\", \"from\": 5715, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"that ideal bubble\", \"from\": 5744, \"to\": 5761}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a6\", \"from\": 5770, \"to\": 5771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu grew up in New Jersey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s capital city, the second youngest of seven children and the first born in the U.S.\", \"from\": 5780, \"to\": 5891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 5780, \"to\": 5782}, {\"ngram\": \"New Jersey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s capital city\", \"from\": 5794, \"to\": 5821}, {\"ngram\": \"seven children\", \"from\": 5846, \"to\": 5860}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 5883, \"to\": 5891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her parents and her five older siblings had fled their war-torn homeland in what is now South Sudan and settled in the Garden State near relatives.\", \"from\": 5892, \"to\": 6039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her parents\", \"from\": 5892, \"to\": 5903}, {\"ngram\": \"her five older siblings\", \"from\": 5908, \"to\": 5931}, {\"ngram\": \"their war-torn homeland\", \"from\": 5941, \"to\": 5964}, {\"ngram\": \"South Sudan\", \"from\": 5980, \"to\": 5991}, {\"ngram\": \"the Garden State\", \"from\": 6007, \"to\": 6023}, {\"ngram\": \"relatives\", \"from\": 6029, \"to\": 6038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Mu (pronouncedmoe) kids traveled as a group, whether to school or church on Sundays.\", \"from\": 6040, \"to\": 6128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pronouncedmoe\", \"from\": 6048, \"to\": 6061}, {\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6087}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 6100, \"to\": 6106}, {\"ngram\": \"church\", \"from\": 6110, \"to\": 6116}, {\"ngram\": \"Sundays\", \"from\": 6120, \"to\": 6127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But only two runners separated from the familial pack.\", \"from\": 6129, \"to\": 6183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only two runners\", \"from\": 6133, \"to\": 6149}, {\"ngram\": \"the familial pack\", \"fro