844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S. record\", \"from\": 6465, \"to\": 6480}, {\"ngram\": \"an indoor 600-meter race\", \"from\": 6485, \"to\": 6509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, she set the U-20 world indoor record in the 800 meters.\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U-20 world indoor record\", \"from\": 6528, \"to\": 6556}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800 meters\", \"from\": 6560, \"to\": 6574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Offers to turn pro started to flood in.\", \"from\": 6576, \"to\": 6615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t ready, not yet.\\u00c2 No matter how fast she ran, Mu always managed to find more speed.\", \"from\": 6616, \"to\": 6711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6674, \"end\": 6676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 6616, \"to\": 6618}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6643, \"to\": 6644}, {\"ngram\": \"more speed\", \"from\": 6699, \"to\": 6709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Trenton Central High, where she played tenor sax, made the honor roll and won a seat on the student council, she tried to have half of a normal existence: She devouredGrey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Anatomy, dabbled in photography and interior design, joined the volunteer club.\", \"from\": 6712, \"to\": 6970, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trenton Central High\", \"from\": 6715, \"to\": 6735}, {\"ngram\": \"tenor sax\", \"from\": 6754, \"to\": 6763}, {\"ngram\": \"the honor roll\", \"from\": 6770, \"to\": 6784}, {\"ngram\": \"a seat\", \"from\": 6793, \"to\": 6799}, {\"ngram\": \"the student council\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 6822}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 6842, \"to\": 6846}, {\"ngram\": \"a normal existence\", \"from\": 6850, \"to\": 6868}, {\"ngram\": \"devouredGrey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Anatomy\", \"from\": 6874, \"to\": 6898}, {\"ngram\": \"photography and interior design\", \"from\": 6911, \"to\": 6942}, {\"ngram\": \"the volunteer club\", \"from\": 6951, \"to\": 6969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t normal on the track; she competed for a club team rather than her high school.\", \"from\": 6971, \"to\": 7066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 6998, \"to\": 7007}, {\"ngram\": \"a club team\", \"from\": 7026, \"to\": 7037}, {\"ngram\": \"her high school\", \"from\": 7050, \"to\": 7065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She needed the competition.\", \"from\": 7067, \"to\": 7094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 7078, \"to\": 7093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She enrolled at Texas A&M on scholarship, set the NCAA outdoor 800 mark and ran the second-fastest 800 ever as a freshman.\", \"from\": 7095, \"to\": 7217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7111, \"end\": 7116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9999372684919878, \"rank\": 4.8022904408332596e-05, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 7117, \"end\": 7120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Henson_Company_Lot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.989436014995498e-48, \"text\": \"A&M\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Henson_Company_Lot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Henson_Company_Lot\"}, {\"begin\": 7145, \"end\": 7149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.939813045222535e-16, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scholarship\", \"from\": 7124, \"to\": 7135}, {\"ngram\": \"a freshman\", \"from\": 7206, \"to\": 7216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was at peace with myself,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 7218, \"to\": 7261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 7218, \"to\": 7222}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 7230, \"to\": 7235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m blessed with this gift.\", \"from\": 7262, \"to\": 7294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 7262, \"to\": 7270}, {\"ngram\": \"this gift\", \"from\": 7284, \"to\": 7293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t take it for granted.\", \"from\": 7295, \"to\": 7325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m here for a reason.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Sure, she had watched the Rio Games as a 14-year-old and thought,I want to be an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 7326, \"to\": 7453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reason.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Sure\", \"from\": 7341, \"to\": 7358}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rio Games\", \"from\": 7376, \"to\": 7389}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 7432, \"to\": 7451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that quickly?\", \"from\": 7454, \"to\": 7471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At 19?\", \"from\": 7472, \"to\": 7478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t think like that.\", \"from\": 7479, \"to\": 7507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 7479, \"to\": 7481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe were just normal,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 7508, \"to\": 7544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\", \"from\": 7508, \"to\": 7513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNormal, ordinary youth club.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Normal meant joy.\", \"from\": 7545, \"to\": 7598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ordinary youth club.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Normal\", \"from\": 7556, \"to\": 7586}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 7593, \"to\": 7596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And joy meant speed.\", \"from\": 7599, \"to\": 7619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 7603, \"to\": 7606}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 7613, \"to\": 7618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Winning had never been Mu\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s problem.\", \"from\": 7621, \"to\": 7659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"problem\", \"from\": 7651, \"to\": 7658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Winningtoo oftenwould be.\", \"from\": 7660, \"to\": 7685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Mu qualified for the Tokyo Games, local officials hung a banner outside city hall in Trenton.\", \"from\": 7687, \"to\": 7785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7692, \"end\": 7694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}, {\"begin\": 7777, \"end\": 7784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\", \"score\": 0.8894944214207702, \"rank\": 0.1242341446081344, \"text\": \"Trenton\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 7709, \"to\": 7724}, {\"ngram\": \"local officials\", \"from\": 7726, \"to\": 7741}, {\"ngram\": \"a banner outside city hall\", \"from\": 7747, \"to\": 7773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many prepped for Olympic viewing parties and celebrated her as theirs, as them.\", \"from\": 7786, \"to\": 7865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic viewing parties\", \"from\": 7803, \"to\": 7826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu delivered, but in delivering, she paid a higher-than-expected toll.\", \"from\": 7866, \"to\": 7936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 7866, \"to\": 7868}, {\"ngram\": \"a higher-than-expected toll\", \"from\": 7908, \"to\": 7935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two years after the Olympics she let slip in one interview what she had known, inside, ever since those magical Games concluded.This pressure was different.She had always embraced the gravity of competition but needed time to adjust to the unfathomable stress often baked into greatness, all the eyeballs and attention, flashing lights and clicking cameras, not to mention the negativity swamps known as social media.\", \"from\": 7938, \"to\": 8355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 7954, \"to\": 7966}, {\"ngram\": \"one interview\", \"from\": 7983, \"to\": 7996}, {\"ngram\": \"those magical Games\", \"from\": 8036, \"to\": 8055}, {\"ngram\": \"This pressure\", \"from\": 8066, \"to\": 8079}, {\"ngram\": \"the gravity\", \"from\": 8118, \"to\": 8129}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 8133, \"to\": 8144}, {\"ngram\": \"needed time\", \"from\": 8149, \"to\": 8160}, {\"ngram\": \"the unfathomable stress\", \"from\": 8174, \"to\": 8197}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 8215, \"to\": 8224}, {\"ngram\": \"all the eyeballs\", \"from\": 8226, \"to\": 8242}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 8247, \"to\": 8256}, {\"ngram\": \"lights\", \"from\": 8267, \"to\": 8273}, {\"ngram\": \"clicking cameras\", \"from\": 8278, \"to\": 8294}, {\"ngram\": \"the negativity swamps\", \"from\": 8311, \"to\": 8332}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 8342, \"to\": 8354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skeptics\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094there weren\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t many, but enough to catch her attention\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094began circling, especially after her performance at the worlds.\", \"from\": 8356, \"to\": 8488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"attention\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094began circling\", \"from\": 8413, \"to\": 8439}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 8458, \"to\": 8473}, {\"ngram\": \"the worlds\", \"from\": 8477, \"to\": 8487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overwhelmed, she focused on the negative aspects of excellence, standards now so high they seemed impossible to meet.\", \"from\": 8490, \"to\": 8607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the negative aspects\", \"from\": 8518, \"to\": 8538}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 8542, \"to\": 8552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t some top-five NFL draft pick.\", \"from\": 8608, \"to\": 8650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8635, \"end\": 8638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999991987352, \"rank\": 4.60281953113316e-10, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was a track star, a big deal in a niche space, largely ignored by mainstream sports fans outside of Olympic years.\", \"from\": 8651, \"to\": 8769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a track star\", \"from\": 8659, \"to\": 8671}, {\"ngram\": \"a big deal\", \"from\": 8673, \"to\": 8683}, {\"ngram\": \"a niche space\", \"from\": 8687, \"to\": 8700}, {\"ngram\": \"mainstream sports fans\", \"from\": 8721, \"to\": 8743}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic years\", \"from\": 8755, \"to\": 8768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But breaking through the track bubble, sprinting so fast as to attract year-round attention, didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t make things better.\", \"from\": 8770, \"to\": 8891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track bubble\", \"from\": 8791, \"to\": 8807}, {\"ngram\": \"year-round attention\", \"from\": 8841, \"to\": 8861}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 8877, \"to\": 8883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It made things worse.\", \"from\": 8892, \"to\": 8913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 8900, \"to\": 8906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt goes beyond just being a great athlete,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mu says.\", \"from\": 8914, \"to\": 8971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 8914, \"to\": 8919}, {\"ngram\": \"a great athlete\", \"from\": 8943, \"to\": 8958}, {\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 8963, \"to\": 8965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBecause, again, there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s expectations, there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s pressure; just eyes being put on you.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Whether she could take the figurative baton fromFelix, becoming not just a face of the U.S. team but the primary one, no longer seemed like a fair question.Felix\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s legacywas defined by longevity, consistency over not years but decades.\", \"from\": 8972, \"to\": 9304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBecause\", \"from\": 8972, \"to\": 8982}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s expectations\", \"from\": 8991, \"to\": 9013}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s pressure\", \"from\": 9015, \"to\": 9033}, {\"ngram\": \"eyes\", \"from\": 9040, \"to\": 9044}, {\"ngram\": \"you.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 9058, \"to\": 9065}, {\"ngram\": \"the figurative baton\", \"from\": 9089, \"to\": 9109}, {\"ngram\": \"fromFelix\", \"from\": 9110, \"to\": 9119}, {\"ngram\": \"just a face\", \"from\": 9134, \"to\": 9145}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. team\", \"from\": 9149, \"to\": 9162}, {\"ngram\": \"the primary one\", \"from\": 9167, \"to\": 9182}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair question\", \"from\": 9206, \"to\": 9221}, {\"ngram\": \"longevity\", \"from\": 9253, \"to\": 9262}, {\"ngram\": \"consistency\", \"from\": 9264, \"to\": 9275}, {\"ngram\": \"not years\", \"from\": 9281, \"to\": 9290}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 9295, \"to\": 9302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there was Mu, fracturing, cracking, fed up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094after a single, exceptional Olympics.\", \"from\": 9305, \"to\": 9391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9319, \"end\": 9321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fracturing\", \"from\": 9323, \"to\": 9333}, {\"ngram\": \"a single, exceptional Olympics\", \"from\": 9360, \"to\": 9390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe was,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Arceneaux says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cin a space where it weighed on her.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Instead of running with joy, like she once did, Mu grew more and more serious, then more and more dark, the sentiment never clearer than in Budapest.\\u00c2 It was time for a break.\\u00c2 She started off with a real vacation\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094no running, no tracks.\", \"from\": 9393, \"to\": 9707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9515, \"end\": 9517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\", \"from\": 9393, \"to\": 9399}, {\"ngram\": \"Arceneaux\", \"from\": 9408, \"to\": 9417}, {\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 9430, \"to\": 9437}, {\"ngram\": \"her.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 9458, \"to\": 9465}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 9490, \"to\": 9493}, {\"ngram\": \"the sentiment\", \"from\": 9570, \"to\": 9583}, {\"ngram\": \"Budapest\", \"from\": 9606, \"to\": 9614}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 9615, \"to\": 9616}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 9624, \"to\": 9628}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 9633, \"to\": 9640}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 9641, \"to\": 9642}, {\"ngram\": \"a real vacation\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094no running\", \"from\": 9664, \"to\": 9692}, {\"ngram\": \"no tracks\", \"from\": 9694, \"to\": 9703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the 2023 worlds she went back to Trenton, back to family and a simpler life, her commitments slimmed way down.\", \"from\": 9708, \"to\": 9824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9747, \"end\": 9754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\", \"score\": 0.8894944214207702, \"rank\": 0.1242341446081344, \"text\": \"Trenton\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2023 worlds\", \"from\": 9714, \"to\": 9729}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 9764, \"to\": 9770}, {\"ngram\": \"a simpler life\", \"from\": 9775, \"to\": 9789}, {\"ngram\": \"her commitments\", \"from\": 9791, \"to\": 9806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She visited a sibling in North Dakota.\", \"from\": 9825, \"to\": 9863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9850, \"end\": 9862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Dakota\", \"score\": 0.9972474879280626, \"rank\": 0.002760106766024367, \"text\": \"North Dakota\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Dakota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Dakota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sibling\", \"from\": 9837, \"to\": 9846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She felt safe in both places, found comfort there.\", \"from\": 9864, \"to\": 9914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both places\", \"from\": 9881, \"to\": 9892}, {\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 9900, \"to\": 9907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu got off social media, replacing online trolling with supportive, familiar voices.\", \"from\": 9915, \"to\": 9999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 9915, \"to\": 9917}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 9926, \"to\": 9938}, {\"ngram\": \"online trolling\", \"from\": 9950, \"to\": 9965}, {\"ngram\": \"supportive, familiar voices\", \"from\": 9971, \"to\": 9998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She read the Bible and prayed daily.\", \"from\": 10000, \"to\": 10036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Bible\", \"from\": 10009, \"to\": 10018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took walks, slowing down.\", \"from\": 10037, \"to\": 10066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"walks\", \"from\": 10046, \"to\": 10051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d never done that before.\", \"from\": 10067, \"to\": 10098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 10067, \"to\": 10074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The break, she says, formed one long, deep breath.\", \"from\": 10100, \"to\": 10150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The break\", \"from\": 10100, \"to\": 10109}, {\"ngram\": \"one long, deep breath\", \"from\": 10128, \"to\": 10149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twice, while shopping in Santa Monica, strangers stopped her.\", \"from\": 10152, \"to\": 10213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10177, \"end\": 10189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\", \"score\": 0.9955564702597874, \"rank\": 0.004463345740644025, \"text\": \"Santa Monica\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"strangers\", \"from\": 10191, \"to\": 10200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One congratulated Mu on her performance in Budapest.\", \"from\": 10214, \"to\": 10266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10257, \"end\": 10265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.745023976496267e-21, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 10232, \"to\": 10234}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 10238, \"to\": 10253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other asked if he could hug her, and\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0089\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0089of course he could!\", \"from\": 10267, \"to\": 10335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"and\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0089\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\", \"from\": 10304, \"to\": 10313}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 10319, \"to\": 10325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t care how you do; we just love you,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said, with no idea how much she needed his support.\", \"from\": 10336, \"to\": 10442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\", \"from\": 10336, \"to\": 10341}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 10402, \"to\": 10409}, {\"ngram\": \"his support\", \"from\": 10430, \"to\": 10441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those positive interactions underscored her ratio of supporters to skeptics.\", \"from\": 10443, \"to\": 10519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those positive interactions\", \"from\": 10443, \"to\": 10470}, {\"ngram\": \"her ratio\", \"from\": 10483, \"to\": 10492}, {\"ngram\": \"supporters\", \"from\": 10496, \"to\": 10506}, {\"ngram\": \"skeptics\", \"from\": 10510, \"to\": 10518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu had been focused on the wrong people, the infinitely smaller segment.\", \"from\": 10520, \"to\": 10592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 10520, \"to\": 10522}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong people\", \"from\": 10543, \"to\": 10559}, {\"ngram\": \"the infinitely smaller segment\", \"from\": 10561, \"to\": 10591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day, she felt a pinch more centered, more grounded.\", \"from\": 10594, \"to\": 10651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pinch\", \"from\": 10614, \"to\": 10621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She started to see that stretch for what it was\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a time of transition, rather than a referendum on her track soul.\\u00c2 She still wanted to win, break records and run faster than ever before.\", \"from\": 10652, \"to\": 10841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that stretch\", \"from\": 10671, \"to\": 10683}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 10704, \"to\": 10708}, {\"ngram\": \"transition\", \"from\": 10712, \"to\": 10722}, {\"ngram\": \"a referendum\", \"from\": 10736, \"to\": 10748}, {\"ngram\": \"her track soul\", \"from\": 10752, \"to\": 10766}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 10767, \"to\": 10768}, {\"ngram\": \"break records\", \"from\": 10794, \"to\": 10807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She still wanted to define her career by all she could accomplish.\", \"from\": 10842, \"to\": 10908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 10869, \"to\": 10879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Mu realized she ran fastest and won most when she ran happy.\", \"from\": 10909, \"to\": 10973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 10913, \"to\": 10915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Worrying about all the ancillary nonsense only made winning harder, less jubilant.\", \"from\": 10974, \"to\": 11056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the ancillary nonsense\", \"from\": 10989, \"to\": 11015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She shaped her new training schedule with intention: She would train year-round, but also build in regular breaks.\\u00c2 \\u00c2 Soon, Mu sensed the return of \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cmy true self.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d In the months and weeks that followed, the sadness infiltrating her joyful existence dripped away.\", \"from\": 11057, \"to\": 11324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11182, \"end\": 11184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her new training schedule\", \"from\": 11068, \"to\": 11093}, {\"ngram\": \"intention\", \"from\": 11099, \"to\": 11108}, {\"ngram\": \"regular breaks\", \"from\": 11156, \"to\": 11170}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00c2\", \"from\": 11171, \"to\": 11174}, {\"ngram\": \"the return\", \"from\": 11191, \"to\": 11201}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cmy true self.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 11205, \"to\": 11224}, {\"ngram\": \"the months\", \"from\": 11228, \"to\": 11238}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 11243, \"to\": 11248}, {\"ngram\": \"the sadness\", \"from\": 11264, \"to\": 11275}, {\"ngram\": \"her joyful existence\", \"from\": 11289, \"to\": 11309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hope returned.\", \"from\": 11325, \"to\": 11339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hope\", \"from\": 11325, \"to\": 11329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nerves dissipated.\", \"from\": 11340, \"to\": 11358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nerves\", \"from\": 11340, \"to\": 11346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She came to view what she overcame as central to her growth.\", \"from\": 11359, \"to\": 11419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her growth\", \"from\": 11408, \"to\": 11418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She returned to a more pragmatic approach, running like that 6-year-old in Trenton ran.\", \"from\": 11420, \"to\": 11507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11495, \"end\": 11502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\", \"score\": 0.8894944214207702, \"rank\": 0.1242341446081344, \"text\": \"Trenton\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trenton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a more pragmatic approach\", \"from\": 11436, \"to\": 11461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she did that, dominance no longer powered her search for purpose and fulfillment.\", \"from\": 11508, \"to\": 11594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dominance\", \"from\": 11527, \"to\": 11536}, {\"ngram\": \"her search\", \"from\": 11555, \"to\": 11565}, {\"ngram\": \"purpose\", \"from\": 11570, \"to\": 11577}, {\"ngram\": \"fulfillment\", \"from\": 11582, \"to\": 11593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the 2023 worlds, Arceneaux arranged a call with a track legend, one who happens to be married to Mu\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s coach.\", \"from\": 11596, \"to\": 11712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2023 worlds\", \"from\": 11602, \"to\": 11617}, {\"ngram\": \"Arceneaux\", \"from\": 11619, \"to\": 11628}, {\"ngram\": \"a call\", \"from\": 11638, \"to\": 11644}, {\"ngram\": \"a track legend\", \"from\": 11650, \"to\": 11664}, {\"ngram\": \"Mu\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s coach\", \"from\": 11699, \"to\": 11711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jackie Joyner-Kersee competed at four Olympics and won a combined six medals, half of them gold, in the heptathlon and long jump.\", \"from\": 11713, \"to\": 11842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11713, \"end\": 11733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Joyner-Kersee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jackie Joyner-Kersee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Joyner-Kersee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Joyner-Kersee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four Olympics\", \"from\": 11746, \"to\": 11759}, {\"ngram\": \"a combined six medals\", \"from\": 11768, \"to\": 11789}, {\"ngram\": \"the heptathlon\", \"from\": 11813, \"to\": 11827}, {\"ngram\": \"long jump\", \"from\": 11832, \"to\": 11841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joyner-Kersee reminded Mu that all the greats lost, slumped or, in the absence of either, faced increasing public pressure borne from lasting success.\", \"from\": 11843, \"to\": 11993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Joyner-Kersee\", \"from\": 11843, \"to\": 11856}, {\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 11866, \"to\": 11868}, {\"ngram\": \"all the greats\", \"from\": 11874, \"to\": 11888}, {\"ngram\": \"the absence\", \"from\": 11910, \"to\": 11921}, {\"ngram\": \"increasing public pressure\", \"from\": 11939, \"to\": 11965}, {\"ngram\": \"lasting success\", \"from\": 11977, \"to\": 11992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The youngest among them, like Mu, were more likely to suffer from that.\", \"from\": 11994, \"to\": 12065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 12024, \"to\": 12026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But fearing that experience wouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t do Mu any good.\", \"from\": 12066, \"to\": 12120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that experience\", \"from\": 12078, \"to\": 12093}, {\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 12108, \"to\": 12110}, {\"ngram\": \"any good\", \"from\": 12111, \"to\": 12119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mu would finish last season, Joyner-Kersee told her, showing their world \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cexactly who you are.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Once she was back on track, Mu had to get backon thetrack.\", \"from\": 12122, \"to\": 12281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12122, \"end\": 12124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}, {\"begin\": 12251, \"end\": 12253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Joyner-Kersee\", \"from\": 12151, \"to\": 12164}, {\"ngram\": \"their world\", \"from\": 12183, \"to\": 12194}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 12243, \"to\": 12248}, {\"ngram\": \"backon thetrack\", \"from\": 12264, \"to\": 12279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her coach suggested she run in a meet she hadn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t even thought about entering.\", \"from\": 12282, \"to\": 12361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her coach\", \"from\": 12282, \"to\": 12291}, {\"ngram\": \"a meet\", \"from\": 12313, \"to\": 12319}, {\"ngram\": \"hadn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 12324, \"to\": 12332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She sent one teammate a text message, asking that they pray.\", \"from\": 12362, \"to\": 12422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one teammate\", \"from\": 12371, \"to\": 12383}, {\"ngram\": \"a text message\", \"from\": 12384, \"to\": 12398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She entered the Prefontaine Classic last September, a surprise to nearly everyone in her sport given how sparingly she had run in 2023.\", \"from\": 12423, \"to\": 12558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Prefontaine Classic\", \"from\": 12435, \"to\": 12458}, {\"ngram\": \"a surprise\", \"from\": 12475, \"to\": 12485}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly everyone\", \"from\": 12489, \"to\": 12504}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 12508, \"to\": 12517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She then set a blistering pace, jockeying with Hodgkinson for positioning and then passing her rival on the final straightaway.\", \"from\": 12559, \"to\": 12686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12606, \"end\": 12616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9995230677747003, \"rank\": 0.00047715979820798815, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a blistering pace\", \"from\": 12572, \"to\": 12589}, {\"ngram\": \"her rival\", \"from\": 12650, \"to\": 12659}, {\"ngram\": \"the final straightaway\", \"from\": 12663, \"to\": 12685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won, holding onto first in a race where the top three women each broke their national record, including Mu, who finished in 1:54.97.\", \"from\": 12687, \"to\": 12823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12795, \"end\": 12797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 12718, \"to\": 12724}, {\"ngram\": \"the top three women\", \"from\": 12731, \"to\": 12750}, {\"ngram\": \"their national record\", \"from\": 12762, \"to\": 12783}, {\"ngram\": \"1:54.97\", \"from\": 12815, \"to\": 12822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In December, on a Zoom call, with the Olympics only seven months away, Mu sounded transformed.\", \"from\": 12825, \"to\": 12919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12896, \"end\": 12898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 12828, \"to\": 12836}, {\"ngram\": \"a Zoom call\", \"from\": 12841, \"to\": 12852}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 12859, \"to\": 12871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI can see everything that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s happening around me,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said.\", \"from\": 12920, \"to\": 12986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 12920, \"to\": 12924}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 12933, \"to\": 12943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy vision, early on, used to be so small.\", \"from\": 12987, \"to\": 13031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy vision\", \"from\": 12987, \"to\": 12999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I see the bigger picture.\", \"from\": 13032, \"to\": 13061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bigger picture\", \"from\": 13042, \"to\": 13060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to appreciate this more.\", \"from\": 13062, \"to\": 13098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 13062, \"to\": 13067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, my God, I have so much gratitude.\", \"from\": 13099, \"to\": 13136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much gratitude\", \"from\": 13118, \"to\": 13135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m just so happy\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094for, like, everything that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s getting ready to come, what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s right at my feet.\", \"from\": 13137, \"to\": 13239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 13137, \"to\": 13142}, {\"ngram\": \"just so happy\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094for\", \"from\": 13143, \"to\": 13162}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 13170, \"to\": 13180}, {\"ngram\": \"my feet\", \"from\": 13231, \"to\": 13238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m just happy to be able to run again.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mu knows who she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s running for and who she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not.\", \"from\": 13240, \"to\": 13339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 13285, \"to\": 13287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She trusts her coach and their training.\", \"from\": 13340, \"to\": 13380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 13351, \"to\": 13360}, {\"ngram\": \"their training\", \"from\": 13365, \"to\": 13379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has never been more consistent, more level, more balanced.\", \"from\": 13381, \"to\": 13443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more consistent, more level\", \"from\": 13400, \"to\": 13427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her relationship to track has never been stronger or healthier.\", \"from\": 13444, \"to\": 13507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her relationship\", \"from\": 13444, \"to\": 13460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arceneaux noticed Mu was running with joy again, that style of competing, he says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthat makes her adorable and why fans will fall in love with her\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d this summer, when the Games unfold.\", \"from\": 13508, \"to\": 13696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13526, \"end\": 13528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arceneaux\", \"from\": 13508, \"to\": 13517}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 13546, \"to\": 13549}, {\"ngram\": \"that style\", \"from\": 13557, \"to\": 13567}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthat\", \"from\": 13591, \"to\": 13598}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 13626, \"to\": 13630}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 13644, \"to\": 13648}, {\"ngram\": \"her\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 13654, \"to\": 13660}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 13679, \"to\": 13688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe best part is,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mu says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m enjoying it in a different way, not on a bad roll but genuinely, like, happy.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Every day since Budapest has pointed Mu towardParis.\", \"from\": 13698, \"to\": 13874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13722, \"end\": 13724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999999994151949, \"rank\": 5.844886024119947e-10, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}, {\"begin\": 13838, \"end\": 13846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.745023976496267e-21, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe best part\", \"from\": 13698, \"to\": 13714}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 13731, \"to\": 13739}, {\"ngram\": \"a different way\", \"from\": 13755, \"to\": 13770}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad roll\", \"from\": 137